---
title: Quickest Crispy Chicken with Cranberry Arugula Salad and Garlic Toasts
description: This chicken doesn’t just cross the road. It races down it at lightning speed. You can have these crispy, breadcrumb-coated cutlets on the table in 20 minutes flat (and that includes the toasty garlic bread and green salad that come on the side). The only thing we suggest slowing down for is savoring all those scrumptious flavors once they’re on your plate.
